node.text:
First season since I came back to my lovely #Seville! I look forward to share more beautiful moments with you! Mention your favorite #goal in the comments! Primera temporada desde que regrese a mi tanto amada #Sevilla! Espero compartir más momentos inolvidables con todos ustedes! Menciona tu gol favorito en los comentarios! ⚽️😍😜🚀
— 
#rakitic #sevillafc #vamosmisevilla @sevillafc

node.text:
#Christmas is about giving. So I decided to share with you some of the best « gifts » that I offered to my team mates. Which one do you prefer? 🎁🎄⚽️🙋🏼‍♂️🎅🏼#IvanRakitic
—
#Navidad es sinónimo de generosidad. En este vídeo les comparto mis mejores asistencias! Cual prefieren?

node.text:
New season, new contest! This time, in collaboration with @uefa_foundation !

We are giving away, 2 tickets for a @championsleague or @europaleague game in your city, 1 signed jersey and 1 pair of signed boots! 🤩🎁

To participate: 
1. Follow my account @ivanrakitic and @uefa_foundation
2. Like this post 
3. Answer this question in the comments: « how many goals did I score during the seasion 20/21?

The winners will be announced on my account and @uefafoundation, on September 19th!

Good luck ! 🍀😁👍🏼
-
#contest #giveaway #rakitic #uefafoundation
